(歐陽文忠公年譜) 知應天府 until 1050.10.23. (歐陽文忠公年譜) In 1055.6.29 made 知蔡州, (續資治通鑑長編/卷180) but didn't go. (墓誌銘) In 1058.7.4 made 知開封府. (續資治通鑑長編/卷187) 知開封府 until 1059.3.19, on that day made 給事中. (歐陽文忠公年譜) 知亳州 until 1068.9.28, on that day made 兵部尚書、知青州，京東東路安撫使. (歐陽文忠公年譜) 知青州 until 1070.5.24, on that day made 判太原府，河東路經略安撫監牧使, but didn't go. (歐陽文忠公年譜 and 墓誌銘) 判太原府 until 1070.8.11, on that day made 知蔡州. (續資治通鑑長編/卷213 and 歐陽文忠公年譜) In 1071.7.10 retired. (歐陽文忠公年譜) In 1072.9.8 died. #渤海丘氏譜牒序 (五代先生文集/渤海丘氏譜牒序)
#丘氏本代北鮮卑人。前燕有毗史那盆低室羅毗者。仕慕容廆為部落酋長、居遼西昌黎郡棘城縣。遂渤海丘氏之先祖。
#酋長後裔毗史那狐字烏狐。皇始元年新興太守。九月從丹陽王慕容買得屯平陶城。己未城降,魏輔國將軍溪牧獲之。送平城、魏太祖依例授大將軍。後爲勃海太守、棘城侯、卒在位。葬勃海郡東光縣，子孫徙家焉。
#孝文帝太和廿年帝詔毗史那改姓丘氏。
#隋末有丘宏字叔襲。清河賊帥竇建德擧兵、宏投建德爲部下。建德自稱長樂王授宏德州刺史。唐高祖殺建德以後劉黑闥攻德州、宏不應逃河南。 唐皇太子破劉黑闥于魏州，山東平宏封東光侯。武德八年受觀州刺史。後去官、卒。 子景崇，襲。
#宏五代孫康天寶中刺史。康生味道味道生克恭克恭生崇崇生宗武宗武、
#丘宗武咸通中刺史。子彥政清泰末刺史
#後丘氏陰德不仕
#崇寧二年同進士出身丘旦、彥政之後裔。始復升家。宣和中試知興元府兼提舉利州路兵馬巡檢事。靖康二年戰金，陣卒。
#興元府公顯忠、子孫萬世恭其德
#紹興十年丘安上寫

taiyuan_murong_005 = { #慕容德豐 Murong Defeng. Second son of Murong Yanzhao. (宋史/卷251) In 977 made 知慶州, where he spent 9 years. (宋史/卷251) 知慶州 in 978.5.4. (續資治通鑑長編/卷019) In 991 made 知邢州. (宋史/卷251) 知邢州 until 992, in that year made 知延州. (宋史/卷251) Later made 知慶州. (宋史/卷251) In 996.7.17 made 知靈州. (續資治通鑑長編/卷039) In 999 made 知鎮州. (宋史/卷251) 知鎮州 until 1000.5.9, on that day made 知滄州. (續資治通鑑長編/卷047) In 1001 made 知貝、瀛二州.  (宋史/卷251)

MacDynasty = {
    name = "Dinh Chi" # Mac Dinh Chi
    dynasty = MacDyn

    # Skills - Known for his scholarship and diplomatic abilities
    diplomacy = 8    # Excellent diplomat
    martial = 3      # Not known for military prowess
    stewardship = 6  # Capable administrator
    intrigue = 4     # Average
    learning = 9     # Renowned scholar

    religion = "phat_giao" # Vietnamese Buddhism was dominant
    culture = "kinh"

    # Traits
    trait = education_learning_4     # Brilliant scholar
    trait = patient                  # Known for his careful thought and wisdom
    trait = shrewd                   # Famous for his wit and intelligence
    trait = humble                   # Rose from humble origins and maintained humility

    1272.1.1 = {
        birth = "1272.1.1"    # Exact date unknown, year confirmed
    }
	1337.1.1 = {
		employer = 1000080084
	}
    1346.1.1 = {
        death = "1346.1.1"    # Exact date unknown, year confirmed
    }
}

1801411 = { #蔡知節 Cai Zhijie. Son of Yi. (蔡氏族譜世系序)
#Son of Yi according to 蔡氏族譜世系序 known also as 宋淳熙四年戡公序 which is acribed to great-grandson of 蔡襄, otherwise well attested 蔡戡. This short preface is contained in the gealogical books of some Cai families, which makes it better classified as para-historical source, rather than historical. There are no offical historical sources which confirm that. The best thing is mention by 歐陽修 on the epitagraph for Cai Xiang that he is a descendant of 蔡克 and that his family was once great, but then diminished in importance. Paradoxically an argument for the authenticity of this preface is its incompletness, between 文表 and his great-great-grandson 劍 there is a lacuna, showing that the author didn't made up everything, as otherwise he would fill them out too. Although, I remain sceptical, I'll accept this document for the purpose of the mod.
	dynasty_house = house_jiyang_cai
	name = "Zhijie_name"
	culture = han
	religion = jingxue
	father = 1801301
	#birth and death dates unknown
	601.1.1 = {
		birth = yes
	}
	664.1.1 = {
		death = yes
	}
}

(資治通鑑/卷275) In 934.10.27 refered as former 潞州節度使, on that day made 安州節度使. (舊五代史/卷46) 安遠節度使 in 937.1.30. 937.1.31 escaped to Wu. 937.3.15 made 宣武節度使 by Wu. (資治通鑑/卷281) In 940.9.5 made 鎮海軍節度使. #Dynasty houses: house_guangping_song 廣平列宋氏, house_fufeng_song 扶風平陵宋氏, house_nanhe_song 南和宋氏, house_qingzhang_song 清漳宋氏, house_putian_song 莆田宋氏

	dynasty = xihe_song_dyn #西河介休宋氏
	name = "Yi_name"
	culture = han
	religion = jingxue

		birth=yes
	}
	-207.1.1 = {
		death = { death_reason = death_execution  }
	}
}

yongqiu_song_082 = { #宋彥筠 Song Yanyun. Eldest son of Song Zhang. (全唐文補遺/第1輯/大周故開府儀同三司太子太師致仕蔡國公贈侍中宋公墓誌銘) After pacification of Former Shu made 維州刺史 [925.12.15-926.3.1]、渝州刺史 [926.3.1-926.6.3]. (墓誌銘) On Mingzong's enthronment made 虢州刺史 [926.6.3-927]. (墓誌銘) In 927 made 武州刺史. (墓誌銘) In 934 made 嚴衛右廂都指揮使、兼和州刺史. (墓誌銘) Later made 萊州刺史 [934-937.8.14]. (墓誌銘) In 937 made 汝州防禦使 [937.8.14]. (墓誌銘) 汝州防禦使 until 939.4.26, on that day made 同州節度使 [until 941.8.19]. (舊五代史/卷78) Former 同州節度使 in 942.10.20, on that day made 鄧州威勝軍節度使. (舊五代史/卷81) 鄧州節度使 until 943.12.2, on that day made 晉州節度使. (舊五代史/卷85) After defeat by Khitan made 靜難軍節度使. (墓誌銘) Former 邠州節度使 in 950.2.14, on that day made 太子太師 and retired. (舊五代史/卷103) In 951.3.15 made 左衛上將軍. (舊五代史/卷111) 左衛上將軍 until 953.7.19, on that day made 太子少師. (舊五代史/卷113) 太子少師 until 954.9.11, on that day retired. (舊五代史/卷114) In 958.9.26 died (舊五代史/卷118) or 956.9.16. (墓誌銘)

###Dunhuang Zhang
#IDs: dunhuang_zhang
#Dynasty: dunhuang_zhang_dyn

dunhuang_zhang_001 = { #張孝嵩 Zhang Xiaosong or 張嵩 Zhang Song. Great-great-grandfather of Zhang Huaicheng. (大唐故朝議郎守鄂王友南陽張府君墓誌銘) In 715 made 沙州刺史. (瓜沙兩郡大事記並序) After 郭虔瓘's death made 安西都護 [or 北庭都護]. (舊唐書/卷103) 北庭都護 in 722.10.29. (新唐書/卷005) 安西都護 until 724, on that day made 太原尹. (舊唐書/卷98) Died at post. (舊唐書/卷103)
	dynasty = dunhuang_zhang_dyn #Dunhuang Zhang
	name = "Xiaosong_name"
	culture = han
	religion = mahayana
	trait = education_martial_3
	trait = jinshi
	#birth and death dates unknown
	660.1.1 = {
		birth = yes
	}
	727.1.1 = {
		death = yes
	}
}
